QuestData.Title: Insurrection
QuestData.Description: First Arcanist Thalyssra has received dark tidings regarding the Nightfallen rebellion and requires your assistance.$b$bJourney to Shal'Aran in Suramar and meet with her.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with First Arcanist Thalyssra in Shal'Aran.
